{"tid":722581,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[莫縮叔台] 智力測驗 - 雷頓教授與魔神之笛 (NDS)","createTime":"2018-06-29T15:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T15:40:28.000Z","uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ed128119edb37ed92f2bae4c5ff1e640ffb7a93d","tid":722581,"uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T15:38:53.000Z","msg":"[莫縮叔台] 智力測驗 - 雷頓教授與魔神之笛 (NDS)<br />\n<br />\n莫縮叔遊戲台<br />\n每個星期五、六、日晚上，<br />\n跟大家一邊傾計，一邊打機<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twitch.tv/mokuncle/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fmokuncle%2F&d=sQfMvwtWSOMjRR2zQj9a0%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ca411288\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.twitch.tv/mokuncle/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/0/05/Professor_Layton_and_the_Last_Specter.jpg/220px-Professor_Layton_and_the_Last_Specter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F0%2F05%2FProfessor_Layton_and_the_Last_Specter.jpg%2F220px-Professor_Layton_and_the_Last_Specter.jpg&h=7784dd68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《雷頓教授與魔神之笛》是由Level-5開發於掌上遊戲機任天堂DS平台的益智冒險電子遊戲。《魔神之笛》是雷頓教授系列的第四作，遊戲劇情發生於系列首作《不可思議城鎮》的三年前，遊戲講述了雷頓教授和他的學生路克&middot;特萊頓相遇的故事。遊戲一共包含170個謎題。 <br />\n<br />\n========================<br />\n莫縮叔Facebook Page: <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/MokUncle\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMokUncle&d=sQfMvwtWSOMjRR2zQj9a0%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=87bc6c7b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/MokUncle</a>"},{"pid":"15ac2af4e70a47140cefc986e8c1cc460b3091f9","tid":722581,"uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T15:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c43b8ca215f4f62b95123afbc2d948cdfb1482